資料準備流程

Fig-3: Data Preparation

Preparing The Predictors (X)

rm(list=ls(all=TRUE))
pacman::p_load(magrittr, caTools, ggplot2, dplyr)
load("data/tf0.rdata") #讀取資料
The Demarcation Date

Remove data after the demarcation date

feb01 = as.Date("2001-02-01")
Z = subset(Z0, date < feb01)    # 618212
Aggregate for the Transaction Records
X = group_by(Z, tid) %>% summarise(
  date = first(date),  # 交易日期
  cust = first(cust),  # 顧客 ID
  age = first(age),    # 顧客 年齡級別
  area = first(area),  # 顧客 居住區別
  items = n(),                # 交易項目(總)數
  pieces = sum(qty),          # 產品(總)件數
  total = sum(price),         # 交易(總)金額
  gross = sum(price - cost)   # 毛利
  ) %>% data.frame  # 88387
summary(X)

Check Quantile and Remove Outlier
sapply(X[,6:9], quantile, prob=c(.999, .9995, .9999)) #check 離群值資料
##          items   pieces     total    gross
## 99.9%  56.0000  84.0000  9378.684 1883.228
## 99.95% 64.0000  98.0000 11261.751 2317.087
## 99.99% 85.6456 137.6456 17699.325 3389.646
X = subset(X, items<=64 & pieces<=98 & total<=11260) # 88387 -> 88295 #去除離群值
Aggregate for Customer Records
d0 = max(X$date) + 1
A = X %>% mutate(
  days = as.integer(difftime(d0, date, units="days")) #取所有交易紀錄與現在差距的天數
  ) %>% 
  group_by(cust) %>% summarise(
    r = min(days),      # recency 
    s = max(days),      # seniority
    f = n(),            # frquency
    m = mean(total),    # monetary
    rev = sum(total),   # total revenue contribution
    raw = sum(gross),   # total gross profit contribution
    age = age[1],       # age group
    area = area[1],     # area code
  ) %>% data.frame      # 28584
nrow(A)
## [1] 28584


Preparing the Target Variables (Y)

Aggregate Feb’s Transaction by Customer
feb = filter(X0, date>= feb01) %>% group_by(cust) %>%  #取出二月購買資料
  summarise(amount = sum(total))  # 16900
The Target for Regression - A$amount A的購買數量

Simply a Left Joint

A = merge(A, feb, by="cust", all.x=T)  #將A購買資料與二月購買資料合併在一起
The Target for Classification - A$buy
A$buy = !is.na(A$amount) #  新增buy的欄位A，判斷A$amount欄位是否有空值。
table(A$buy, !is.na(A$amount)) # NA欄位數=A是否有購買。有的話，可以對應Amount即知道數量。

Preparing Train & Test Datasets

Train & Test Dataset
X = subset(X, cust %in% A$cust & date < as.Date("2001-02-01")) #篩選出2001二月前的資料
Z = subset(Z, cust %in% A$cust & date < as.Date("2001-02-01")) 
set.seed(2018); spl = sample.split(A$buy, SplitRatio=0.7) #用A$buy去切且用0.7的比例七成training 三成test
c(nrow(A), sum(spl), sum(!spl))
## [1] 28584 20009  8575
cbind(A, spl) %>% filter(buy) %>%   #拿train資料(spl)和原始資料(A)看兩者分佈是否一致
  ggplot(aes(x=log(amount))) + geom_density(aes(fill=spl), alpha=0.5)

A2 = subset(A, buy) %>% mutate_at(c("m","rev","amount"), log10) #從A挑出有購買的人
n = nrow(A2)
set.seed(2018); spl2 = 1:n %in% sample(1:n, round(0.7*n))
c(nrow(A2), sum(spl2), sum(!spl2))
## [1] 13245  9272  3973
cbind(A2, spl2) %>%  #拿train資料(spl2)和原始資料(A2)看兩者分佈是否一致
  ggplot(aes(x=amount)) + geom_density(aes(fill=spl2), alpha=0.5)

save(Z, X, A, spl, spl2, file="data/tf3.rdata") #儲存檔案 Z:項目/X:訂單/A:顧客/sp1:所有資料的分割向量/sp2:挑出有購買過的資料的分割向量
